ef08b32933f609ce5b82","tid":528895,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:04:03.000Z","msg":"投馮檢基即係話比泛民知：香港人好滿意"},{"pid":"d5d22cbc64cc04d6f46fa691551cc89a815c6c01","tid":528895,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【新增短片】立法會新界東和九龍西各有1個議席在3月補選，民主派今日設8個票站舉行初選，協調人選出戰。<span style=\"color: red;\">在石硤尾邨票站外，有兩位女選民手持「支持基哥（馮檢基）」及「支持政壇李克勤」的紙牌，其中一位馮檢基支持者盧小姐指，她居住在該區（九龍西），一直支持馮，特意前來投票。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>盧小姐從票站離開時，卻向記者表示票站人員要求記錄她的身分證號碼，她認為身分證號碼是個人私隱，她拒絕交出，所以沒有投票，她直斥有關規定不公平。記者追問她是否上屆都有投票給馮檢基，盧回應「係」，記者告知她馮檢基上屆出選新界西後，她便沒有回應，揚長而去。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今年80多歲的馮婆婆，今午撐著柺扙到石硤尾票站排隊投票，問到今次投票重要性時，馮婆婆說：「我見到有人投票，咪埋嚟投吓囉，我投馮檢基」。問到支持馮檢基的原因時，馮婆婆說：「佢（馮檢基）領導咗咁耐，都咁好，咪選返佢囉」。問到投票過程是否辛苦時，馮婆婆說：「梗辛苦啦，我要撐柺扙」。⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180114/57706258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57706258&d=VJDn%2BW9awTT4qQJ7EVJ3IL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=1f9a4405\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57706258&h=814d5f99\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180114/57706258</a>"},{"pid":"88e70a95e05eee14127e6d29d43e5c4628e547cf","tid":528895,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5d22cbc64cc04d6f46fa691551cc89a815c6c01","tid":528895,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.